lead_paragraph: Jay Cox homered twice to help North Carolina move to the College World Series championship round with a 6-5 victory over Cal State Fullerton last night. The Tar Heels (53-13) won Bracket 1 and will play Rice or Oregon State in the best-of-three finals beginning Saturday.
